        public StaticRouteConfig(java.lang.String name,
                 java.lang.String staticRoute,

        Create a static route configuration with all the information.
        Parameters:
        name - The name (String) of the static route config
        staticRoute - The string representation of the route. e.g. 192.168.1.1/24
        nextHop - The string representation of the next hop IP address. e.g. 10.10.1.1
